def calculate_digit_sum(n: int, m: int) -> int:
    last_digit = m * 10
    l = [last_digit]
    for i in range(1, 10):
        l.append((l[-1] + last_digit) % 10)
    a = n // m
    b = a // 10
    ans = b * sum(l)
    for i in range(a % 10):
        ans += l[i]
    return ans
